snippet.title: EverQuest's 20th Expansion - Call of the Forsaken
snippet.description: Buy Call of the Forsaken and encounter brand new zones such as Bixie Warfront and West Karana.  Get your hands on must-have features like Mercenary AAs/Gear, and Heroic Adventures!   Get yours at https://www.everquest.com/expansion-content
